          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The cross   section   asymmetry   of   the   deuteron",
                " photodisintegration   process   d(g,pn)   has   been",
                " measured in the energy  range  0.3  -  1.0  GeV  for",
                " proton cm angles of 45,  60,  75, and 90 degree. The",
                " data obtained were compared with predictions of  the",
                " existing    theoretical   models,   based   on   the",
                " conventional approach,  as well as with the  results",
                " of  Kharkov  multipole  analysis  which  takes  into",
                " account the  contribution  of  dibaryon  resonances.",
                " Neither  of  these  theoretical models describes the",
                " experimental data satisfactory."
              ]
            }
          ],
